reviews.productTitle: GE Grounding Paddle Rocker Switch 5 Pack, Single Pole, In Wall On/Off Power Switch Replacement for Ceiling Fans & Lights, 15 Amp, Great for Home, Office & Kitchen, UL Listed, White, 44017
reviews.text: Good reviews and low price from a well known brand, GE, but the old adage "you get what you pay for" is true. I have had to replace two out of the five switches, so far. The paddle rocker switch part comes loose and eventually comes off. These are just plastic molded with side clips that apparently give way and no longer hold in place. My youngest son no doubt messed with them and made them worse but never should have come free like they did to allow him to pull one whole paddle free. Not clear if there's a risk of shock with the cover paddle removed but the contact switch is metal under the plastic housing. I will be inspecting the rest and replacing as needed. I do not recommend this product.
reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on October 12, 2021
reviews.title: Needed to replace 2 out of 5 so far
